Check for:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Broken transitions\u8232 \'95 Missing confirmations\u8232 \'95 Confusing state changes\u8232 \'95 Places users are unsure what to do next\u8232 \'95 Inconsistent behavior between similar actions\
